Package: fiRes
Title: Tools for Analyzing and Visualizing NASA FIRMS Fire Detections
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hanna ZoÃ«", "Schulten", email = "hanna.schulten@stud-mail.uni-wuerzburg.de", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: 
    A set of tools for processing, classifying, and visualizing NASA's FIRMS (Fire Information 
    for Resource Management System) fire detection data. Includes spatial classification using 
    OpenStreetMap land use, seasonal grouping, fire frequency estimation, and plotting functions 
    for both spatial and statistical analysis.
